  <num>36-157</num>
  <heading>Actions in tort permissible.</heading>
  <text>Nothing in this subchapter shall prevent or restrain any person who is the legal owner of a trademark or label from proceeding in an action of tort against any person found guilty of violating this subchapter.</text>
